Package gw.api.webservice.importTools

Class ImportResults

java.lang.Object
gw.api.webservice.importTools.ImportResults
All Implemented Interfaces:
GWRemotable, Serializable
public final class ImportResults extends Object implements GWRemotable, Serializable
Class that contains information about the results of an import call. This data structure contains data on which entities were inserted and/or updated, along with any errors that might have occurred during the import.
